================================================================================
IMPORTANT NOTICE REGARDING ROM FILES
================================================================================

This software is a hardware emulation system. It does NOT include any 
copyrighted ROM files from the original computers.

The ROM files for the following systems are required but NOT PROVIDED:
- Commodore 64 (BASIC, KERNAL, CHARGEN)
- VIC-20 (BASIC, KERNAL, CHARGEN)
- Commodore 16 (BASIC, KERNAL)
- ZX Spectrum (48K ROM)
- Apple II (Monitor, BASIC, CHARGEN)
- Atari 800 (OS, BASIC)

Users must obtain these ROM files legally from:
1. Original hardware they own
2. Licensed distributors
3. Official sources where available

The authors of this software do not condone or support piracy.
